                { name: "آيات عن ليلة القدر", nameEn: "Verses about Laylat al-Qadr (97)", color: "yellow",
                    items: [{ar:"إنا أنزلناه في ليلة القدر",en:"We sent it down on the Night of Qadr",verse:"إِنَّا أَنزَلۡنَـٰهُ فِي لَيۡلَةِ ٱلۡقَدۡرِ وَمَآ أَدۡرَىٰكَ مَا لَيۡلَةُ ٱلۡقَدۡرِ لَيۡلَةُ ٱلۡقَدۡرِ خَيۡرٌۭ مِّنْ أَلۡفِ شَهۡرٍ",ref:"97:1-3",verseEn:"Indeed, We sent the Qur'an down during the Night of Decree. And what can make you know what is the Night of Decree? The Night of Decree is better than a thousand months."},{ar:"ليلة القدر خير من ألف شهر",en:"Better than a thousand months",verse:"لَيْلَةُ ٱلۡقَدۡرِ خَيۡرٌ مِّنْ أَلۡفِ شَهۡرٍ تَنَزَّلُ ٱلۡمَلَـٰٓئِكَةُ وَٱلرُّوحُ فِيهَا بِإِذۡنِ رَبِّهِم مِّن كُلِّ أَمۡرٍۢ سَلَـٰمٌ هِيَ حَتَّىٰ مَطۡلَعِ ٱلۡفَجۡرِ",ref:"97:3-5",verseEn:"The Night of Decree is better than a thousand months. The angels and the Spirit descend therein by permission of their Lord for every matter. Peace it is until the emergence of dawn."},{ar:"تنزل الملائكة والروح فيها",en:"Angels and Spirit descend",verse:"تَنَزَّلُ الْمَلَائِكَةُ وَالرُّوحُ فِيهَا بِإِذْنِ رَبِّهِم مِّن كُلِّ أَمْرٍ",ref:"97:4",verseEn:"The angels and the Spirit descend therein by permission of their Lord for every matter."},{ar:"سلام هي حتى مطلع الفجر",en:"Peace until the rise of dawn",verse:"فَإِذَا نُقِرَ فِي ٱلصُّورِ فَلَآ أَنسَىٰ إِلَّا مَن شَآءَ ٱللَّهُ فَصَلِّ لِرَبِّكَ وَٱنۡحَرۡ إِنَّ ٱلَّذِي خَلَقَكَ لَهُۥ وَهُوَ ٱلۡوَٲحِدُ ٱلۡقَهَّارُ وَإِذَا قُرِئَ ٱلۡقُرۡءَانُ فَٱسۡتَمِعُوا۟ لَهُۥ وَأَنصِتُوا۟ لَعَلَّكُمۡ تُرۡحَمُونَ سَلَـٰمٌ هِيَ حَتَّىٰ مَطۡلَعِ ٱلۡفَجۡرِ",ref:"56:8-13, 56:89",verseEn:"So when the Horn is blown, no relationship will there be among them that Day, nor will they ask about one another. Except whom Allah wills. Then [there is] a prayer for your Lord and sacrifice. Indeed, He who created you is ever, over you, a Guardian. And when the Qur'an is recited, then listen to it and pay attention that you may receive mercy. Peace it is until the emergence of dawn."}],
                    verse: {ayah:"إِنَّا أَنزَلْنَاهُ فِي لَيْلَةِ الْقَدْرِ ۝ وَمَا أَدْرَاكَ مَا لَيْلَةُ الْقَدْرِ ۝ لَيْلَةُ الْقَدْرِ خَيْرٌ مِّنْ أَلْفِ شَهْرٍ", en:"Indeed, We sent it down during the Night of Decree. And what can make you know what the Night of Decree is? The Night of Decree is better than a thousand months.", ref:"97:1-3"}},
                { name: "آيات عن الذكر والقرآن", nameEn: "Verses about remembrance and the Quran", color: "green",
                    items: [{ar:"ولقد يسرنا القرآن للذكر",en:"We made the Quran easy to remember (54:17)",verse:"وَلَقَدْ يَسَّرْنَا الْقُرْآنَ لِلذِّكْرِ فَهَلْ مِن مُّدَّكِرٍ ۞ فَذَكِّرْ إِنَّمَا أَنتَ مُذَكِّرٌ",ref:"54:17-18",verseEn:"And We have certainly made the Qur'an easy for remembrance, so is there any who will remember? So remind, [O Muhammad]; you are only a reminder."},{ar:"فاذكروني أذكركم",en:"Remember Me, I will remember you (2:152)",verse:"فَاذْكُرُونِي أَذْكُرْكُمْ وَاشْكُرُوا لِي وَلَا تَكْفُرُونِ",ref:"2:152",verseEn:"So remember Me; I will remember you. And be grateful to Me and do not deny Me."},{ar:"ألا بذكر الله تطمئن القلوب",en:"Hearts find rest in Allah's remembrance (13:28)",verse:"أَلَا بِذِكْرِ اللَّهِ تَطْمَئِنُّ الْقُلُوبُ ۗ الَّذِينَ آمَنُوا وَتَطْمَئِنُّ قُلُوبُهُم بِذِكْرِ اللَّهِ ۗ أَلَا بِذِكْرِ اللَّهِ تَطْمَئِنُّ الْقُلُوبُ",ref:"13:28-29",verseEn:"Unquestionably, by the remembrance of Allah hearts are assured. Those who have believed and whose hearts are assured by the remembrance of Allah. Unquestionably, by the remembrance of Allah hearts are assured."},{ar:"إنا نحن نزلنا الذكر",en:"We sent down the Reminder (15:9)",verse:"إِنَّا نَحْنُ نَزَّلْنَا الذِّكْرَ وَإِنَّا لَهُ لَحَافِظُونَ",ref:"15:9",verseEn:"Indeed, it is We who sent down the Qur'an and indeed, We will be its guardian."}],
                    verse: {ayah:"أَلَا بِذِكْرِ اللَّهِ تَطْمَئِنُّ الْقُلُوبُ", en:"Verily, in the remembrance of Allah do hearts find rest.", ref:"13:28"}},
                { name: "صفات عباد الرحمن", nameEn: "Qualities of servants of Ar-Rahman (25:63-74)", color: "blue",
                    items: [{ar:"يمشون على الأرض هونا",en:"Walk on earth humbly",verse:"وَعِبَادُ الرَّحْمَنِ الَّذِينَ يَمْشُونَ عَلَى الْأَرْضِ هَوْنًا وَإِذَا خَاطَبَهُمُ الْجَاهِلُونَ قَالُوا سَلَامًا",ref:"25:63",verseEn:"And the servants of the Most Merciful are those who walk upon the earth humbly, and when the ignorant address them [harshly], they say [words of] peace."},{ar:"إذا خاطبهم الجاهلون قالوا سلاما",en:"Say 'peace' to the ignorant",verse:"وَعِبَادُ الرَّحْمَنِ الَّذِينَ يَمْشُونَ عَلَى الْأَرْضِ هَوْنًا وَإِذَا خَاطَبَهُمُ الْجَاهِلُونَ قَالُوا سَلَامًا ۝ وَالَّذِينَ يَبِيتُونَ لِرَبِّهِمْ سُجَّدًا وَقِيَامًا",ref:"25:63-64",verseEn:"And the servants of the Most Merciful are those who walk upon the earth humbly, and when the ignorant address them [harshly], they say [words of] peace. And those who spend [part of] the night to their Lord prostrating and standing."},{ar:"يبيتون لربهم سجدا وقياما",en:"Spend nights in worship",verse:"وَالَّذِينَ يَبِيتُونَ لِرَبِّهِمْ سُجَّدًا وَقِيَامًا ۝ وَالَّذِينَ يَقُولُونَ رَبَّنَا اصْرِفْ عَنَّا عَذَابَ جَهَنَّمَ ۖ إِنَّ عَذَابَهَا كَانَ غَرَامًا",ref:"25:64-65",verseEn:"And those who spend the night before their Lord prostrating and standing. And those who say, \"Our Lord, avert from us the punishment of Hell. Indeed, its punishment is ever adhering;"},{ar:"إذا أنفقوا لم يسرفوا",en:"Spend without extravagance",verse:"وَإِذَا أَنفَقُوا لَمْ يُسْرِفُوا وَلَمْ يَقْتُرُوا وَكَانَ بَيْنَ ذَٰلِكَ قَوَامًا",ref:"25:67",verseEn:"And those who, when they spend, do so not excessively or sparingly but are ever, between that, [justly] moderate."}],
                    verse: {ayah:"وَعِبَادُ الرَّحْمَٰنِ الَّذِينَ يَمْشُونَ عَلَى الْأَرْضِ هَوْنًا", en:"And the servants of the Most Merciful are those who walk upon the earth humbly.", ref:"25:63"}},
                { name: "دروس من سورة الكهف", nameEn: "Lessons from Surah Al-Kahf", color: "purple",
                    items: [{ar:"الإيمان والثبات",en:"Faith and steadfastness (Cave)",verse:"وَكَانُوا يُؤْمِنُونَ بِاللَّهِ وَرَسُولِهِ وَيُجَاهِدُونَ فِي سَبِيلِ اللَّهِ بِأَمْوَالِهِمْ وَأَنفُسِهِمْ",ref:"18:14",verseEn:"And they believed in Allah and His Messenger and spent [in the way of Allah] out of that in which He had made them successors. And they were certain [in faith] that they would meet their Lord."},{ar:"فتنة المال",en:"Trial of wealth (Gardens)",verse:"وَفَتْنَةُ الْمَالِ وَالْأَوْلَادِ كَمَثَلِ غَيْثٍ أَعْجَبَ الْكُفَّارَ نَبَاتُهُ",ref:"18:46",verseEn:"And the example of wealth and children is like the example of rain which We send down from the sky that the plants of the earth absorb - [those] from which men and livestock eat - until, when the earth has taken on its adornment and is beautified and its people suppose that they have capability over it, there comes to it Our command by night or by day, and We make it a barren ground, as if it had not flourished yesterday."},{ar:"التواضع في العلم",en:"Humility in knowledge (Khidr)",verse:"قَالَ لَهُ عَالِمٌ مِنْهُمْ آتِينِي بِعَلْمِكَ قَالَ إِنَّ لَدَيَّ مِنْ عِلْمِ الَّذِي لَمْ تُعَلِّمْنِي",ref:"18:65",verseEn:"He said to him, \"A man from among them will come to me and ask me about your knowledge.\" He said, \"Indeed, with me is knowledge about that which you do not teach me.\""},{ar:"القوة والعدل",en:"Power and justice (Dhul-Qarnayn)",verse:"إِنَّا مَكَّنَّا لَهُ فِي الْأَرْضِ وَآتَيْنَاهُ مِنْ كُلِّ شَيْءٍ سَبَبًا فَأَتْبَعَ سَبَبًا",ref:"18:84",verseEn:"Indeed, We established him upon the earth, and We gave him to everything a way."}],
                    verse: {ayah:"وَاصْبِرْ نَفْسَكَ مَعَ الَّذِينَ يَدْعُونَ رَبَّهُم بِالْغَدَاةِ وَالْعَشِيِّ يُرِيدُونَ وَجْهَهُ", en:"And keep yourself patient with those who call upon their Lord in the morning and evening, seeking His countenance.", ref:"18:28"}}
